{
  "texts": [
    "For the diploid progenitors, to allow interspecies comparisons, the mapping was done to each of the subgenomes separately, including chromosome zero, that is, contigs not assembled into pseudo mole cules, in both mappings.",
    "Joint calling was carried out using GenotypeGVCFs (GATK) 107 and snpEff v.4.3t was used to assess the impact of the SNPs 108.",
    "To remove regions with cross-species mappings, we removed the SNPs that were called as heterozygous when mapping the di-haploid ET-39 sequencing data to the Arabica reference genome.",
    "Genome-wide nucleotide diversity was calculated with vcftools v.0.1.17 (ref.",
    "109), by calculating the mean of pi values from sliding windows of 100 kb with 10-kb step size."
  ]
}